{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"selected"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"animated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"animated"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" if the view should display itself as selected; "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if it should display itself as unselected."}]}],"name":"selected"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":" if the change in selection state is animated; ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":" if the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"change is immediate.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"animated"}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You should not call this method directly. A map view calls this method in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"response to user interactions with the annotation. Subclasses may override this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method in order to customize the appearance of the view depending on its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"selection state."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples","level":4,"type":"heading"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setselected:animated:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the selection state of the annotation view with an optional animation."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setSelected:animated:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"title":"setSelected:animated:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:animated:"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L230","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"},"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:animated:"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)setSelected:animated:","symbolKind":"method"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"title":"MLNAnnotationView","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/setSelected:animated:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:animated:"}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:animated:"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the selection state of the annotation view with an optional animation."}],"title":"setSelected:animated:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setselected:animated:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setSelected:animated:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/AnnotationViewExample":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/annotationviewexample","title":"Custom Annotation View","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Add a custom annotation view"}],"type":"topic","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample","role":"article"}}}